\id TIT  
\h TAITUS 
\toc1 Taitus 
\toc2 Taitus 
\toc3 Taitus 
\mt1 Taitus  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Aya Pol, Negur nẽ ferfer, Jesus Kristus nẽ aposel, Negur igirnẽdin neid momoiya nigin ado, momoi nẽ keleĩ uyu irou di, idi fateul bagai dibodõf nigin, igirnan,  
\v 2 momoiya ado keleĩ anĩ, mata faimud ibodkeleya nẽ wau iseya bun ibodok, mata faimud ibodkeleya anĩ nigin Negur ĩ to idegẽdig, fau sain gariya inoya sã mog, wau kuturol fen, promis od iron.  
\v 3 Agef fen, yogon sain bun bagai, Negur neda Isennadaya ĩ irõ di, aya biya od wogõya kabĩ ifanan anĩ bunem wogõ au di, in od yaoren,   
\p
\v 4 Taitus, neu kesu bagai, ada momoiya tekelei ado õ bun pas enei atotof:  
\p Negur Tamada ado Kristus Jesus neda Isennadaya neid wau ifenẽya ado wau inosiya õ bun ibodõf.   
\s1 Taitus Nẽ Kabĩ Oun Krit Nuyo  
\p
\v 5 Aya Krit nuyo an atornon anĩ nẽ gariya are, ereb bure felediya san anĩ madur woid fen, taun ganan bun uyu irouya, aya õ orokonon gen ugirnẽdiyouf nigin.  
\v 6 Uyu irouya are ĩ bouwa od sã, kayau tekelei aiwa, tamo ĩ ne gere tar momoiya ado, tetẽya, idodõya sã.  
\v 7 Sios lo fiya tamo ĩ, Negur nẽ kabĩ ifenẽya nigin, ĩ bouwa od sã, to aya dogol yedig, kaisã to name isedig, aai fatuk to yõdig, to kusĩ yedig, idegẽya bunem safina to yaledig.  
\v 8 Agef mã, ĩ tamo yaledig, ereb biya nigin wau laa fedig, ĩ kisi biya ado ibodõdig, madur, fateul, ĩ yogo nigin biya kulatun fedig.  
\v 9 Ĩ momoiya od difelnen anĩ irou kafĩ falauf, anĩ bunem, ĩ sã tunĩ keleĩ biya bunem waud yalesauf, agef fen, ĩ idi keleĩ biya od nigin kiwai dinon anidi faded fiyẽdiyouf bagai.   
\p
\v 10 Ere nigin, an idodõya tamo, od kaũ sã, idegẽya temeleid musei difaref, idi atun mulũ bun temeleid anidim age difedig bagai.  
\v 11 Idi sigoreid ufofãf, ere nigin, idi idegẽya bunem safina yaleya nigin to ifelnẽya nẽ anĩ difelneĩd fen, fõ fõ adok daũ difedif.  
\v 12 Idi neid fonõ profet taka eig ye iron, “Krit tamo kayau idi faimud idegẽya temeleid, gaar kuĩ sane gen, fõ temeleid saaf weweneid.”  
\v 13 Od enei are momoi. Anĩ nigin, totol od urokeneĩd, ou wiyẽdiyouf, ago di, anĩ idi neid momoiya biyauf,  
\v 14 anĩ bunem, idi Juda neid nenerĩ kaũ sã to karĩ douf, age de fen, idi momoi nẽ anĩ ditoron anidi neid od to dõ difouf.  
\v 15 Karẽ bun temeleid bun, ereb ereb ganan karẽ, anĩ ere, idi amuyẽ kisi ado momoiya sã anidi bun, karẽ taka sã. Momoi, idi neid waud ado kisi es fiya sane len.  
\v 16 Idi Negur keleĩ dedig, anĩ ere, nedi tobonuneid bun, idi Negur nigin wa difedig. Idi sane bagai, idodõya temeleid, idi ereb biya age fiya nigin kisi feleya sã.   
\c 2  
\s1 Ereb Mala Fire Fire Ifelnẽdiyauf  
\p
\v 1 Õ ereb biya od wogõ yef anĩ kilei ufelnẽdiyouf.  
\v 2 Tamo biyeid dogo nigin biya kulatun difouf nigin, idi anĩ karĩ difiyẽdiyouf nigin, idi kisi biya ado dibodõf nigin ado, momoiya, waud laa fiya ado, feseya sã ifareya bun madur dibodõf nigin ufelnẽdiyouf bagai.   
\p
\v 3 Age fiya bagai, kayau biyeideg karĩ del dibodõf nigin, taka dumen od to dirõf nigin, wain fatuk bagai to dãf nigin, agef fen, ereb biya anĩ difelnẽdiyouf nigin ufelneĩd.  
\v 4 Ago di, idi, kayau momoul, nedi aiweid tar adodo kesu tar nigin waud laa fouf nigin, tai difediyouf,  
\v 5 idi dogo nigin, sã biya kulatun difouf nigin ado bouweid od sã dibodõf nigin, fõ bun kabĩ dalouf nigin, tobonunã biya age difouf nigin ado, aiweid tar nigin karĩ difediyouf, age dife di, taka nem Negur nẽ od to kobu fouf nigin, kayau momoul tai difediyouf.   
\p
\v 6 Age fiya gen bagai, kesu gaũ, dogo nigin biya kulatun difouf nigin wedereid urou.  
\v 7 Ereb ereb ganan bun, idi dile fen, dõ difouf nigin ereb ereb biya ago. Ogon ifelnẽya bun, õ tutuk ifareya, wau adok ifelnẽdiya bun ifenẽya,  
\v 8 wogõ biya tamo to kiwai difenẽf nẽ anĩ ufelnẽdiyouf, ago di, idi kiwai difonok anĩ mama fediyouf, ere nigin, idi ada nigin ereb sane taka wogõya nigin are sã.   
\p
\v 9 Ferfer, ereb ereb ganan bun, nedi moroid tar karĩ difediyouf, waud al fiya difenẽdiyouf, aiteid to solo difouf,  
\v 10 idi bun tamal bẽ to dalouf, idi nedi moroid tar nẽ od dõ fiya biya bagai anĩ difelnẽdiyouf nigin ufelnẽdiyouf, age dife di, naab ganan bun, idi age difef bunem, Negur neda Isennadaya nigin ifelnẽya anĩ, tamo meleid bun biya ile di, tamo neid oroya anĩ bun dinouf.   
\p
\v 11 Negur nẽ wau ifenẽya, isennẽya irou isidig anĩ, tamo ganan bun isin.  
\v 12 Anim, Negur nẽ tobonunã dõ fiya sã ado tenebur nẽ oroya sane bun, “Bai” yeya nigin ifelnadadig, agef fen, ada dug nigin biya kulatun ibodõya, madur ibodõya ado, Negur nẽ oroya bun, gama sain enei bun ibodõya nigin, ifelnadadig,  
\v 13 agef mã, ada el fiya nẽ wauda iseya, are neda Negur odug ado Isennadaya, Jesus Kristus ĩ, fula fiya medeĩya ado isiyouf anĩ tarĩ tafouf,  
\v 14 Jesus Kristus ĩ yogo luwa ada nigin itoron, are ĩ sesen ganan bun tamal yalelnada fen, ĩ yogo nigin yogon tamo kayau bagai kulo fele di, idi ereb biya age difouf nigin kabĩ totol dalouf nigin, ĩ age fen.   
\p
\v 15 Ereb ereb enei õ ufelnẽdiyouf. Ogon totol ganan bunem, idi neid waud wales fen, wedereid urou. To loloum weid len, õ lai diyõf.   
\c 3  
\s1 Ereb Biya Anĩ Dõf Age Fouf  
\p
\v 1 Tamo kayau wedereid fokõ wo, are idi lo fiya ado yeneid adodo tamo karĩ difediyouf, to didodõf, idi biya age difouf nigin ololo difouf,  
\v 2 taka to bouwa bun od dũf, wau inosiya ado waud difenẽdiyouf, tamo ganan bun dimatkesiyouf nigin ago.   
\p
\v 3 Adag kulu kisi neneya adon, tadodon, didegnadan, tenebur nẽ oroya fire fire ado bouwa nẽ oroya fire fire nẽ ferfer tabodon. Ada tobonunã sesen ado kiyeĩ bun tabodon, to dileda orodin, adag taileid to orodan.  
\v 4 Anĩ ere, Negur neda Isennadaya nẽ tobonunã biya ado wau laa fiya wõ ye fen,  
\v 5 ĩ isennadan, are ada ereb madur age tafen anĩ bunem sã, are yogon wau yũya bunem. Ĩ mata wõya nẽ naan kulo fiya bunem ado, Awa Uur Fateulem mata falei fiya bunem isennadan.  
\v 6 Negur ĩ, Jesus Kristus neda Isennadaya bunem, Awa Uur Fateul, ada bun kisi feleya bagai foula fen,  
\v 7 are yogon wau ifenẽya bunem madur fadan, anĩ bunem, ada mata faimud ibodkeleya nẽ wauda iseya ado fen, in akor anĩ talouf nigin age fen.  
\v 8 Od enei momoi bagai, anĩ nigin, aya, õ enei totol wogõ wo di, Negur nigin momoi def anidi karĩ del fen, ereb biya anĩ el de age difouf anĩ orouf. Enei ganan are biya bagai, tamo ganan nigin deuf.   
\p
\v 9 Anĩ ere, neneya kisi abob fe fiyẽya anĩ, ibor dir fiya, monẽya ado, lo nigin luwa irouya anĩ sese wiyeĩd, ere nigin, anidi are kaũ sã, kabĩ ifenẽya kisi feleya sã.  
\v 10 Taka ĩ, ã atun fara fef, uruwa bun weder urouwauf, ago fen, babaneg weder urouwauf. Anĩ bure fele di, ĩ utornẽf.  
\v 11 Õ keleĩ youf, tamo age fiya are wau gogil fen, mosor bun ilen, ĩ yogo bouwa sanen inon.   
\s1 Idikeleya Nẽ Od  
\p
\v 12 Sain aya õ gein Artemas be Tikikus sur afiyẽ di, õ Nikopolis an, aya gein kaisã isiya nigin, totol bagai naab umirẽf, ere nigin, yau sain bun aya an abodõf nigin kisi anon.  
\v 13 Lo keleĩ tamo Senas ado Apolos, idi neid naab dilauf nigin, ereb ereb ganan usennẽdiyouf, ago di, idi ereb lau fiya sã dilauf.  
\v 14 Neda tamo kayau idig, ereb ereb biya age fiya nigin, idi de keleĩ anĩ dalouf bagai, are idi naa ganan nẽ safina dale fen, kaũ sã to dibodõf nigin age difouf.   
\p
\v 15 Ganan aya geid mabodok anidim, õ bun aanya sur mafef. Momoiya bun amã nigin waud laa fef anidi aan wiyeĩd.  
\p Wau ifenẽya ã ganan bun ibodõf.   